title: International Factball: Iran v Argentina v Ecuador
content: The QI Elves in association with www.visitengland.com bring you the fourteenth episode of International Factball - the only football podcast that has absolutely nothing to do with football.Today in this never-before-tried three-way special, Dan Schreiber (@schreiberland), Anna Ptaszynski (@nosuchthing), James Harkin (@jamesharkin) and Freddy Soames (@fsoames), pit Iran against Argentina against Ecuador to find out which is the most Quite Interesting country.
